OL,5, Airline passengers on UK domestic      
OL,6, flights are being promised a fairer and
OL,7, simpler compensation process for delays
OL,8, under proposals announced on Monday.   
OL,10,FThe new rules would mean travellers    
OL,11,Fcould claim for delays of more than an 
OL,12,Fhour, whereas currently they have to   
OL,13,Fhave been held up for over three hours.
OL,15,FThe plans would replace EU compensation
OL,16,Frules the UK retained after Brexit.    
OL,18,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps said  
OL,19,Fthe proposals "aim to bolster airline  
OL,20,Fconsumer protections and rights".      
